5️⃣ INTERVENTION ENGINE
🟡 L1 — Soft Guidance
Suggestions based on signal thresholds:
    • Review easy-first strategy
    • Reinforce phase discipline
    • Revise weak topics
    • Practice structured pacing
No mention of enforcement.

🔵 L2 — Structural Intervention
Trigger logic:
If Impulsive cluster > 35%
→ Suggest Controlled Mode
If Overstay > threshold
→ Suggest Hard Mode (limited)
If Phase Deviation > 30%
→ Suggest Phase Training
If Easy Neglect > 40%
→ Suggest Easy-First Template design
Card example:
“Batch B: 41% Impulsive risk. Recommend Controlled Mode next mock.”
Interventions stored as:
interventionRecommendations/{academicYear}
Never auto-applied.

